note: this is just an initial thought about how the projects' structure nothing is certain!

this is how the project is PROBABBLY gonna be structured:

webserv/
├── Makefile                      # C++98 build with -Wall -Wextra -Werror
├── include/
│   ├── server/
│   │   ├── Server.hpp            # Main server class (handles multiple ports)
│   │   ├── Connection.hpp        # Client connection state (non-blocking I/O)
│   │   ├── EventLoop.hpp         # epoll implementation (since Linux)
│   │   └── IMultiplexer.hpp      # Abstract I/O multiplexing interface
│   ├── config/
│   │   ├── ConfigParser.hpp      # Recursive descent parser for config
│   │   ├── ServerConfig.hpp      # Server block (host/port/error_pages)
│   │   ├── RouteConfig.hpp       # Location block (methods/redir/CGI)
│   │   └── Directive.hpp         # Tokenized config directives
│   ├── http/
│   │   ├── Request.hpp           # HTTP request parsing (chunked support)
│   │   ├── Response.hpp          # HTTP response generation
│   │   ├── StatusCodes.hpp       # HTTP status codes (RFC-compliant)
│   │   ├── MimeTypes.hpp         # Content-Type mappings
│   │   └── UploadHandler.hpp     # File upload processing
│   ├── cgi/
│   │   ├── CGIHandler.hpp        # CGI execution (with timeout)
│   │   ├── CGIEnvironment.hpp    # Environment variable setup
│   │   └── CGIRunner.hpp         # Bonus: Multiple CGI dispatcher
│   ├── utils/
│   │   ├── Logger.hpp            # Thread-safe logging
│   │   ├── FileUtils.hpp         # File operations (dir listing, sanitization)
│   │   ├── StringUtils.hpp       # String manipulation (trim/split)
│   │   ├── URI.hpp               # URI parsing and normalization
│   │   ├── SocketUtils.hpp       # Socket helper functions
│   │   └── MemoryUtils.hpp       # Custom allocator (for stability)
│   └── bonus/                    # Bonus features
│       ├── session/
│       │   ├── SessionManager.hpp # Cookie/session storage
│       │   └── Session.hpp        # Session data model
│       └── auth/                  # Auth extensions (if implemented)
├── src/
│   ├── main.cpp                  # Entry point (config loading)
│   ├── server/
│   │   ├── Server.cpp            # Server initialization
│   │   ├── Connection.cpp        # I/O handling (epoll-ready only)
│   │   └── EventLoop.cpp         # epoll event processing
│   ├── config/
│   │   ├── ConfigParser.cpp      # Syntax tree construction
│   │   ├── ServerConfig.cpp      # Server block validation
│   │   └── RouteConfig.cpp       # Route rule processing
│   ├── http/
│   │   ├── Request.cpp           # Request parsing (with chunk decode)
│   │   ├── Response.cpp          # Response building (autoindex/CGI)
│   │   └── UploadHandler.cpp     # File upload handling
│   ├── cgi/
│   │   ├── CGIHandler.cpp        # CGI execution (non-blocking pipes)
│   │   └── CGIEnvironment.cpp    # RFC-compliant env setup
│   ├── utils/
│   │   ├── Logger.cpp            # Timestamped logging
│   │   ├── FileUtils.cpp         # Path traversal prevention
│   │   └── URI.cpp               # URI decoding/encoding
│   └── bonus/
│       ├── session/
│       │   ├── SessionManager.cpp# Cookie persistence
│       │   └── Session.cpp       # Session expiration
│       └── cgi/CGIRunner.cpp     # Bonus: Multi-CGI handler
├── test/
│   ├── test_configs/             # Config test cases
│   │   ├── invalid/
│   │   ├── multi_server.conf
│   │   └── upload_route.conf
│   ├── stress_tests/             # Load testing
│   │   ├── siege_benchmark.sh
│   │   └── wrk_scripts/
│   ├── browser_tests/            # Frontend tests
│   │   ├── file_upload.html
│   │   └── session_test.html     # Bonus test
│   ├── unit_tests/               # Component tests
│   │   ├── test_ConfigParser.cpp
│   │   └── test_Request.cpp
│   └── cgi_scripts/              # CGI test binaries
│       ├── test.py
│       ├── test.php
│       └── upload_handler.pl      # Bonus: Multi-CGI test
├── configs/
│   ├── default.conf              # Reference config
│   ├── mime.types                # Official IANA types
│   └── error_pages/
│       ├── 400.html
│       ├── 403.html
│       ├── 404.html
│       └── 500.html
└── docs/
    ├── DESIGN.md                 # Architecture decisions
    ├── EPROTOCOL.md              # epoll workflow
    └── BONUS.md                  # Session/CGI bonus docs